          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_1294246486234524747.png",
                "id": "talent92961",
                "key": "碎涛旋跃",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "碎涛旋跃"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，此角色每有3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">无尽食欲</span>提供的额外最大生命，此伤害+1（最多+5）。然后<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span>1张原本元素骰费用最高的手牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/923db325e73849fb31b138dfdd1a0cab_7787913629348327683.png",
                "id": "talent3381",
                "key": "迸落星雨",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "迸落星雨"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>，对敌方所有后台角色造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>。召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">黑色幻影</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/dec2f5cea15b6652638355fb66ef2d98_6218065411786567826.png",
                "id": "talent89121",
                "key": "横噬鲸吞",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "横噬鲸吞"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">深噬之域</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/edd2da5186218246a20f5b0d52d2c634_6368911911534862858.png",
                "id": "talent89776",
                "key": "无尽食欲",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "无尽食欲"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">入场时：</span>获得我方已吞噬卡牌中最高元素骰费用值的「攻击力」，获得该费用的已吞噬卡牌数量的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段和我方宣布结束时：</span>造成此牌「攻击力」值的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方出战角色受到伤害时：</span>抵消1点伤害，然后此牌<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>-2。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_138087306968869234.png",
                "id": "talent75802",
                "key": "黑色幻影",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/bc781100ebefe81947d3fac533aaed65_1819035799175269457.png",
                "title": "黑色幻影"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_5563445536839899095.png",
                "id": "talent98668",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">深噬之域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>我方<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">调和</span>的手牌，会被吞噬。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">每吞噬3张牌：</span>吞星之鲸获得1点额外最大生命；如果其中存在原本元素骰费用值相同的牌，则额外获得1点；如果3张均相同，再额外获得1点。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span></strong></p><p>通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">调和</span></strong></p><p>为了进行元素调和，而将行动牌从手牌中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_479988223309419672.png",
                "id": "talent99106",
